1
00:02:07,710 --> 00:02:08,520
You're here.

2
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,870
You really know how to enjoy yourself.

3
00:02:10,870 --> 00:02:11,530
Have a seat.

4
00:02:14,030 --> 00:02:14,560
Try this.

5
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,960
It arrived this morning.

6
00:02:18,870 --> 00:02:21,079
Are we really going to be locked up here?

7
00:02:21,310 --> 00:02:23,000
Is there no other way out?

8
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:25,240
I can't think of any other way for now.

9
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,280
Instead of thinking about that,

10
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,240
we might as well

11
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,640
fill our stomachs first.

12
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:31,400
You're really good at comforting yourself.

13
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:33,079
Instead of feeling sorry for yourself,

14
00:02:33,079 --> 00:02:35,010
think about something wonderful.

15
00:02:36,630 --> 00:02:37,960
What wonderful things?

16
00:02:39,430 --> 00:02:41,560
I think right now is pretty wonderful.

17
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:44,240
Right now is wonderful?

18
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,150
Yeah.

19
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,870
The villagers are all saved.

20
00:02:49,870 --> 00:02:51,400
We've returned safely.

21
00:02:51,470 --> 00:02:52,400
Isn't that good?

22
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,360
If we can get out,

23
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,520
what do you want to do?

24
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:00,080
The incident in Huangpi Village

25
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:02,210
showed me the suffering of the people.

26
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,870
If I could open a clinic,

27
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:06,280
I would definitely be able
to save more people.

28
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:06,910
Yeah.

29
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,010
That sounds quite nice.

30
00:03:10,430 --> 00:03:12,120
What's the use of it being nice?

31
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,680
Being stuck here now,

32
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:16,570
thinking or worrying
about anything is useless.

33
00:03:27,430 --> 00:03:28,310
You drank it?

34
00:03:30,030 --> 00:03:30,890
Don't swallow.

35
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,310
Wine.

36
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,160
Calm down.

37
00:03:42,710 --> 00:03:43,240
Don't!

38
00:03:50,630 --> 00:03:51,630
Don't.

39
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,440
Don't, don't, don't.

40
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:01,870
Are you tired?

41
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,190
Be good.

42
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,620
Let's go. Let's get some rest.

43
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:07,600
What's...

44
00:04:08,190 --> 00:04:09,030
What's wrong?

45
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:12,730
Han Yunling.

46
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:23,390
Giddy up! Off to battle!

47
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,680
Just one lap.

48
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,800
Han Yunling.

49
00:04:46,190 --> 00:04:47,190
You know what?

50
00:04:48,270 --> 00:04:50,070
This courtyard you hate the most

51
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:53,680
is the place I dream of the most.

52
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,120
Xiao Chi.

53
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:00,070
Yeah.

54
00:05:07,630 --> 00:05:09,040
I want to...

55
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,980
What's wrong with you?

56
00:07:01,270 --> 00:07:03,510
I got a stiff neck.

57
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,360
Last night,

58
00:07:06,950 --> 00:07:08,480
did I torture you

59
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,270
again?

60
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,390
No.

61
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:13,070
You just fell asleep
after drinking too much.

62
00:07:13,070 --> 00:07:14,930
I made some congee for you. Try it.

63
00:07:19,070 --> 00:07:20,330
Isn't this burnt rice?

64
00:07:20,870 --> 00:07:21,310
It's just

65
00:07:21,310 --> 00:07:23,310
some dry congee.

66
00:07:23,310 --> 00:07:24,510
It's okay. It's okay.

67
00:07:25,190 --> 00:07:26,600
I like burnt rice too.

68
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,830
That's good.

69
00:07:27,830 --> 00:07:29,000
Then try it.

70
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,270
I have some dishes inside.

71
00:07:36,270 --> 00:07:37,830
Let me go check.

72
00:07:59,390 --> 00:08:00,430
You are here.

73
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:01,960
I came to take a look.

74
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:03,870
Look.

75
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,920
Just add some water, and it'll be fine.

76
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:08,870
Add some water.

77
00:08:11,270 --> 00:08:12,270
General Xiao.

78
00:08:12,270 --> 00:08:13,950
Are you sure this

79
00:08:13,950 --> 00:08:15,040
is edible?

80
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,000
Before cooking,

81
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,560
it was definitely edible.

82
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,720
But now,

83
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,450
I think it should still be fine.

84
00:08:22,830 --> 00:08:23,960
It's cooked anyway.

85
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:25,720
It seems for these few days,

86
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:27,480
I'll have to take charge of the meals.

87
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,680
Otherwise, I'll either be poisoned

88
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,630
or starved to death by you.

89
00:08:29,630 --> 00:08:30,160
Sure.

90
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:30,750
I'll be your assistant.

91
00:08:30,750 --> 00:08:31,510
Can you chop vegetables?

92
00:08:31,510 --> 00:08:32,080
I can.

93
00:09:18,630 --> 00:09:20,120
Xiao Chi.

94
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,440
I told you to chop the vegetables,

95
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:23,150
not murder them.

96
00:09:23,270 --> 00:09:25,440
I might have used a bit too much force.

97
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,480
Just go out first.

98
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:34,960
Stop making a mess in here.

99
00:09:38,150 --> 00:09:39,360
Just sit here.

100
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,200
Don't move around.

101
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:40,870
Okay.

102
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,510
I promise

103
00:09:46,510 --> 00:09:47,570
I won't move at all.

104
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,630
I'm watching you.

105
00:10:23,910 --> 00:10:24,870
All the dishes are ready.

106
00:10:24,870 --> 00:10:25,510
Great.

107
00:10:26,510 --> 00:10:28,080
It's just a simple home-cooked meal.

108
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,000
Make do with it.

109
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,460
It's already very hearty.

110
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:31,960
When I was in the military camp,

111
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,360
we only had canteen food.

112
00:10:39,270 --> 00:10:40,080
Thank you.

113
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,750
Try this.

114
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:57,240
Your Majesty,

115
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,510
Xiao Chi and Han Yunling

116
00:10:58,510 --> 00:11:00,240
cured the villagers of Huangpi Village.

117
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:01,840
They are meritorious subjects
who have served the state well.

118
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:03,480
Why, after returning,

119
00:11:03,750 --> 00:11:05,630
did they end up being grounded?

120
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,480
Lord Fei.

121
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:09,270
Don’t be such an alarmist.

122
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:12,120
They returned from that infected village.

123
00:11:12,270 --> 00:11:14,390
We just let them stay at home

124
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,440
temporarily.

125
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:17,630
How is that being grounded?

126
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:18,790
Lord Wang,

127
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:19,870
haven't seen you for a few days.

128
00:11:19,870 --> 00:11:21,000
You truly look radiant

129
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,460
and flushed with success.

130
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,150
Your Majesty,

131
00:11:24,150 --> 00:11:25,360
I think

132
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:27,240
what Lord Wang said makes sense.

133
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,630
Xiao Chi stayed in Huangpi Village

134
00:11:28,630 --> 00:11:30,120
for many days.

135
00:11:30,270 --> 00:11:32,910
Although the villagers seem cured now,

136
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,910
just in case,

137
00:11:35,030 --> 00:11:36,320
having them stay at home

138
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,720
to avoid contact for a while

139
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:39,910
is very necessary.

140
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:40,880
Your Majesty,

141
00:11:41,150 --> 00:11:43,080
I also think it makes a lot of sense.

142
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,080
Lord Fei,

143
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,000
do not waste

144
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:47,080
Lord Zhang's good intentions.

145
00:11:48,390 --> 00:11:49,670
What you said

146
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,580
is not without reason.

147
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:54,570
But General Xiao
has made great contributions.

148
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,200
I plan to let him

149
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:59,200
leave his residence
during my marriage alliance ceremony.

150
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:01,320
I will personally host
a welcome banquet for him

151
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,910
as a reward.

152
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:06,270
And that

153
00:12:06,270 --> 00:12:07,150
Physician Han.

154
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:08,670
She is the one you brought back

155
00:12:08,670 --> 00:12:10,240
from Tianlang Pass?

156
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,480
Your Majesty,

157
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:13,480
exactly.

158
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:15,540
It is Han Yunling from Tianlang Pass.

159
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:16,910
When I have the chance,

160
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:18,450
I will see her in person.

161
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:19,910
Yes.

162
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:22,000
I...

163
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,730
Thank you again, Your Majesty,

164
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:26,000
for letting me enter the palace once more.

165
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:28,870
I really couldn't stay at home anymore.

166
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:31,500
How could I have forgotten about you?

167
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:34,270
Why did I let you enter the palace?

168
00:12:34,790 --> 00:12:36,720
With the mistakes you made before,

169
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:39,960
you should reflect on yourself at home.

170
00:12:40,790 --> 00:12:42,190
If there's nothing else,

171
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,680
don't come out again.

172
00:12:45,550 --> 00:12:46,360
Your Majesty.

173
00:12:50,510 --> 00:12:52,200
This...

174
00:12:56,910 --> 00:12:57,870
I'm done.

175
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:59,510
General Xiao, you wash the dishes.

176
00:12:59,510 --> 00:13:00,120
Me?

177
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:01,670
What?

178
00:13:02,150 --> 00:13:05,000
You don't even know
how to wash dishes, General Xiao?

179
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:06,630
How could I not know how to wash dishes?

180
00:13:06,630 --> 00:13:07,230
I'll do it.

181
00:13:26,670 --> 00:13:27,720
What's wrong?

182
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:30,670
My hand slipped.

183
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:34,240
Why weren't you more careful?

184
00:13:58,790 --> 00:14:00,910
Xiao Chi, did you do that on purpose?

185
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:25,510
My...

186
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:26,960
neck.

187
00:14:29,120 --> 00:14:30,240
Oh.

188
00:14:31,790 --> 00:14:33,550
Go get some rest.

189
00:14:33,550 --> 00:14:34,910
I'll clean it up.

190
00:14:34,910 --> 00:14:36,200
I know.

191
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:38,400
Don't worry, I'll clean everything up.

192
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:44,630
By the Mandate of Heaven,
the Emperor decrees:

193
00:14:44,630 --> 00:14:48,910
the 9th day of this month is chosen
as the auspicious day for the grand wedding,

194
00:14:48,910 --> 00:14:53,910
to be officiated by the Ministry of Rites
and the Astronomical Bureau.

195
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:56,600
This proclamation is hereby
announced to the world.

196
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:58,720
By Imperial Command.

197
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:03,270
Xiao Chi and Han Yunling,
accept the decree.

198
00:15:03,270 --> 00:15:04,930
I accept the Imperial Decree.

199
00:15:06,270 --> 00:15:09,080
This time, Xiao Chi and Han Yunling
have done their best to cure the epidemic.

200
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,200
You have made outstanding achievements.

201
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,600
You are truly pillars of the state

202
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:12,870
and a blessing to the people.

203
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:14,240
The quarantine period is now over.

204
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:15,270
The pestilence has dissipated.

205
00:15:15,270 --> 00:15:15,840
Decree:

206
00:15:15,840 --> 00:15:18,600
Xiao Chi and Han Yunling
are to enter the palace immediately

207
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:20,870
to receive rewards and titles
before the throne.

208
00:15:20,870 --> 00:15:21,720
By Imperial Command.

209
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:23,510
I accept the decree.

210
00:15:27,910 --> 00:15:29,270
Alright, please rise.

211
00:15:33,630 --> 00:15:34,760
You're finally out.

212
00:15:35,270 --> 00:15:36,400
There's still time.

213
00:15:36,510 --> 00:15:37,170
His Majesty

214
00:15:37,510 --> 00:15:38,910
has been hoping every day that you could

215
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:41,080
make it to his marriage alliance ceremony.

216
00:15:41,080 --> 00:15:41,960
Of course.

217
00:15:42,080 --> 00:15:44,280
We will go together when the time comes.

218
00:15:47,270 --> 00:15:48,240
Then I

219
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:49,970
won't disturb you anymore.

220
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:51,320
I'll take my leave.

221
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:51,870
Okay.

222
00:15:54,510 --> 00:15:55,320
Sigh.

223
00:15:58,390 --> 00:15:59,520
Where are you going?

224
00:15:59,790 --> 00:16:00,630
We've been released.

225
00:16:00,630 --> 00:16:01,840
I should hurry up and go.

226
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:03,840
I've had enough of staying with you.

227
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:12,750
Jin Xi.

228
00:16:12,750 --> 00:16:13,270
Yes.

229
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:15,480
Physician Han and General Xiao

230
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:17,880
have been ground
for almost a month, right?

231
00:16:18,910 --> 00:16:20,570
It's exactly one month today.

232
00:16:21,840 --> 00:16:22,840
It's been so long.

233
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:24,790
If I were locked up for this long,

234
00:16:24,790 --> 00:16:26,590
I don't know what I would become.

235
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:30,480
You would look like me now.

236
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:32,940
Physician Han.

237
00:16:33,510 --> 00:16:35,040
Greetings, Your Highness.

238
00:16:35,150 --> 00:16:36,440
When did you get out?

239
00:16:36,510 --> 00:16:37,550
Just now.

240
00:16:37,720 --> 00:16:39,750
I came to see you as soon as I got out.

241
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:41,600
You must have been bored to death.

242
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:43,480
Having food and drink was nice.

243
00:16:43,630 --> 00:16:45,000
I was bored out of my mind.

244
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:47,120
Mainly because of that annoying Xiao Chi.

245
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:48,200
It was a nightmare.

246
00:16:48,750 --> 00:16:49,280
Let's go.

247
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:50,200
I have some good food in my room.

248
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:50,910
Your Highness,

249
00:16:50,910 --> 00:16:51,720
you go first.

250
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,130
I'll find you later.

251
00:16:53,790 --> 00:16:54,240
Okay.

252
00:16:57,910 --> 00:16:58,720
Jin Xi.

253
00:17:05,069 --> 00:17:07,000
This is the medicine
I prepared for you recently.

254
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:08,680
I hope it helps you.

255
00:17:30,270 --> 00:17:31,200
Father.

256
00:17:31,830 --> 00:17:33,400
Why did you teach me the way

257
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:35,000
of an emperor back then?

258
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:38,510
I am a woman.

259
00:17:40,070 --> 00:17:41,790
Even if I never marry,

260
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:45,250
I have no chance of inheriting the throne.

261
00:17:46,070 --> 00:17:46,920
Father,

262
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:49,400
why does everyone
in Jinglan listen to you?

263
00:17:49,480 --> 00:17:50,350
Xie,

264
00:17:50,590 --> 00:17:51,720
to govern a country,

265
00:17:51,750 --> 00:17:53,480
you need not only firm methods,

266
00:17:53,720 --> 00:17:55,310
but also flexible wisdom.

267
00:17:55,310 --> 00:17:56,590
Only by coupling firmness with gentleness

268
00:17:56,590 --> 00:17:57,310
can you

269
00:17:57,400 --> 00:17:58,720
stabilize the court.

270
00:17:58,920 --> 00:18:00,270
The way of an emperor

271
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:01,680
and the art of managing people

272
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:02,720
lie in balance.

273
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:03,680
Father,

274
00:18:03,680 --> 00:18:05,240
I also want to be a wise ruler,

275
00:18:05,240 --> 00:18:06,270
just like you.

276
00:18:07,480 --> 00:18:08,510
Do you

277
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:11,790
want me to assist Liu Chu forever?

278
00:18:16,480 --> 00:18:18,070
What an old fox.

279
00:18:27,590 --> 00:18:28,510
Your Highness,

280
00:18:29,510 --> 00:18:31,510
if Jiang Wanyu enters the palace,

281
00:18:31,790 --> 00:18:33,350
will His Majesty still

282
00:18:33,350 --> 00:18:34,880
listen to you as he does now?

283
00:18:37,310 --> 00:18:38,640
When people grow up,

284
00:18:39,400 --> 00:18:40,880
they won't listen.

285
00:18:41,510 --> 00:18:42,720
Then what

286
00:18:43,070 --> 00:18:44,070
should we do?

287
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:50,140
As the Eldest Princess of the Liu family,

288
00:18:50,880 --> 00:18:53,280
I must prioritize the family's interests.

289
00:18:53,310 --> 00:18:53,880
It's best

290
00:18:54,680 --> 00:18:56,720
if she can have another child
as soon as possible.

291
00:18:56,720 --> 00:18:58,550
As long as the Liu family's children

292
00:18:58,550 --> 00:19:00,200
are all under my control,

293
00:19:01,350 --> 00:19:03,280
the empire will be secure forever.

294
00:19:09,550 --> 00:19:10,550
Old fox.

295
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,510
Don't forget

296
00:19:13,720 --> 00:19:15,480
I am your daughter.

297
00:19:46,640 --> 00:19:47,500
Your Highness.

298
00:19:47,550 --> 00:19:48,070
Mhm.

299
00:19:48,790 --> 00:19:50,850
The wedding procession has arrived.

300
00:20:01,790 --> 00:20:03,440
The palace isn't like the outside.

301
00:20:03,440 --> 00:20:04,770
Don't run around later.

302
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:06,270
I know.

303
00:20:14,440 --> 00:20:15,510
The time has come.

304
00:20:16,070 --> 00:20:17,930
Welcome the Princess of Changmo.

305
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:15,480
The late Emperor decreed:

306
00:21:15,480 --> 00:21:16,920
Beyond the Great Wall,

307
00:21:16,920 --> 00:21:18,320
the King of Mo shall rule.

308
00:21:18,590 --> 00:21:19,880
Within the Great Wall,

309
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:21,680
the officials of the court shall preside.

310
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:23,070
It is also decreed

311
00:21:23,510 --> 00:21:24,640
that let the people

312
00:21:24,640 --> 00:21:27,070
farm and weave, or hunt
for their food and clothing.

313
00:21:27,070 --> 00:21:28,480
Families shall not be separated,

314
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:30,000
rulers and subjects shall live in peace,

315
00:21:30,000 --> 00:21:31,270
and there shall be no tyranny.

316
00:21:31,270 --> 00:21:33,590
Today, our two nations
are united in a peace alliance.

317
00:21:33,590 --> 00:21:35,480
We lay down our arms
from this day forward.

318
00:21:35,480 --> 00:21:38,140
May there be eternal peace
for all generations!

319
00:22:26,400 --> 00:22:27,270
Today

320
00:22:27,750 --> 00:22:29,440
is the marriage alliance ceremony

321
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:32,750
between me, Liu Chu,
and Princess Jiang Wanyu of Changmo.

322
00:22:33,640 --> 00:22:34,920
From now on,

323
00:22:34,920 --> 00:22:36,680
the two nations will lay down the spear

324
00:22:36,680 --> 00:22:37,880
and open trade.

325
00:22:38,790 --> 00:22:40,030
From today forward,

326
00:22:40,310 --> 00:22:41,270
Jinglan

327
00:22:41,270 --> 00:22:42,240
and Changmo

328
00:22:43,030 --> 00:22:45,000
shall remain friends for generations,

329
00:22:45,000 --> 00:22:46,920
enjoying everlasting peace!

330
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:49,030
Remain friends for generations,

331
00:22:49,030 --> 00:22:50,920
enjoying everlasting peace.

332
00:22:50,920 --> 00:22:52,830
Remain friends for generations,

333
00:22:52,830 --> 00:22:55,070
enjoying everlasting peace.

334
00:22:55,070 --> 00:22:57,000
Remain friends for generations,

335
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:59,070
enjoying everlasting peace.

336
00:22:59,510 --> 00:23:00,370
Your Highness.

337
00:23:00,960 --> 00:23:02,110
He is really looking more and more

338
00:23:02,110 --> 00:23:03,200
like an emperor.

339
00:23:04,880 --> 00:23:05,680
Indeed.

340
00:23:06,510 --> 00:23:09,030
His Majesty is looking more
and more like the late emperor.

341
00:23:09,030 --> 00:23:10,890
Remain friends for generations,

342
00:23:10,920 --> 00:23:12,510
enjoying everlasting peace.

343
00:23:12,510 --> 00:23:15,030
If Father could see this scene today,

344
00:23:17,030 --> 00:23:18,720
he would surely be happy.

345
00:23:19,240 --> 00:23:21,310
Today is His Majesty's big day.

346
00:23:21,510 --> 00:23:24,000
Would you like to go and join the fun?

347
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:27,920
Today,

348
00:23:28,680 --> 00:23:30,080
he is the main character.

349
00:23:30,510 --> 00:23:32,830
I won't go and join the fun.

350
00:23:42,590 --> 00:23:44,590
This ceremony really exhausted me.

351
00:23:49,030 --> 00:23:50,200
In Changmo,

352
00:23:50,790 --> 00:23:52,030
even when high-ranking officials
marry off their daughters,

353
00:23:52,030 --> 00:23:54,030
there isn't such a grand spectacle.

354
00:23:55,310 --> 00:23:56,910
It seems my father was right.

355
00:23:57,200 --> 00:23:59,200
Liu Chu really put his heart into it.

356
00:24:03,920 --> 00:24:06,200
I'm going to share a bed with him tonight.

357
00:24:10,070 --> 00:24:12,310
What did my father teach me?

358
00:24:14,310 --> 00:24:16,070
A woman’s virtue comes first.

359
00:24:16,310 --> 00:24:18,200
Her words should be cautious.

360
00:24:18,310 --> 00:24:19,830
Her appearance proper.

361
00:24:20,310 --> 00:24:21,920
The husband leads, the wife follows.

362
00:24:21,920 --> 00:24:23,270
United in heart—

363
00:24:23,270 --> 00:24:24,200
One man guarding the pass

364
00:24:24,200 --> 00:24:25,060
is as good as...

365
00:24:25,640 --> 00:24:26,720
No.

366
00:24:27,510 --> 00:24:28,920
I forgot it all.

367
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:36,070
Let me have a bite to eat first.

368
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:57,880
His Majesty arrives!

369
00:25:34,960 --> 00:25:36,030
Today,

370
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:37,700
you must be exhausted.

371
00:25:42,510 --> 00:25:43,480
According...

372
00:25:43,480 --> 00:25:45,480
According to Jinglan's customs,

373
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:47,830
we use this ceremonial weighing rod

374
00:25:48,110 --> 00:25:50,310
to lift the bride's veil.

375
00:25:55,480 --> 00:25:56,480
Okay.

376
00:26:19,310 --> 00:26:20,200
Are

377
00:26:21,680 --> 00:26:22,350
you ready?

378
00:26:33,270 --> 00:26:34,130
I'm lifting it.

379
00:27:03,510 --> 00:27:04,590
Why is it you?

380
00:27:04,830 --> 00:27:06,070
Why can't it be me?

381
00:27:06,070 --> 00:27:07,440
Aren't you General Xiao's—

382
00:27:07,440 --> 00:27:08,310
Older brother.

383
00:27:09,160 --> 00:27:10,110
Xiao Chi

384
00:27:10,200 --> 00:27:11,240
grew up without a mother.

385
00:27:11,240 --> 00:27:12,400
When we were young,

386
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:14,440
he, Fei Zheng, and I grew up together
in the Prince's Mansion,

387
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:15,550
and we kowtowed

388
00:27:15,550 --> 00:27:17,080
and became sworn brothers.

389
00:27:17,480 --> 00:27:19,200
Xiao Chi is the third.

390
00:27:19,310 --> 00:27:20,640
Fei Zheng is the second.

391
00:27:20,720 --> 00:27:21,780
And I am the eldest.

392
00:27:22,240 --> 00:27:23,030
I didn't lie to you,

393
00:27:23,030 --> 00:27:23,830
did I?

394
00:27:24,240 --> 00:27:26,500
No wonder you wouldn't tell me your name.

395
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:40,550
Then tell me

396
00:27:41,030 --> 00:27:42,240
now,

397
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:44,590
what is my name?

398
00:27:45,270 --> 00:27:46,240
Liu Chu.

399
00:27:50,030 --> 00:27:51,440
Then tell me,

400
00:27:52,680 --> 00:27:53,590
what am I

401
00:27:54,070 --> 00:27:55,830
to you now?

402
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:58,880
My husband.

403
00:28:02,920 --> 00:28:04,000
Are you surprised?

404
00:28:05,440 --> 00:28:06,440
No.

405
00:28:07,070 --> 00:28:08,030
It's a shock.

406
00:28:12,270 --> 00:28:13,800
Then let me shock you again.

407
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:41,720
Your Majesty,

408
00:28:42,030 --> 00:28:44,200
I have an urgent matter to report.

409
00:28:52,830 --> 00:28:53,750
Lord Zhang,

410
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:55,270
what is it so late at night?

411
00:28:55,270 --> 00:28:56,070
Your Majesty,

412
00:28:56,480 --> 00:28:58,880
this concerns the state.

413
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:00,880
I dared not delay for a moment.

414
00:29:00,960 --> 00:29:02,960
Since Lord Zhang is looking for you,

415
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:04,310
you should go.

416
00:29:05,310 --> 00:29:06,070
Alright.

417
00:29:06,550 --> 00:29:07,310
I will

418
00:29:07,790 --> 00:29:08,680
be right back.

419
00:29:08,680 --> 00:29:09,200
Okay.

420
00:29:18,070 --> 00:29:19,640
So he is Liu Chu.

421
00:29:23,440 --> 00:29:24,590
Your Majesty.

422
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:25,750
Changmo

423
00:29:25,750 --> 00:29:27,240
has sent a letter.

424
00:29:27,310 --> 00:29:29,350
They said that,
since the marriage alliance is complete,

425
00:29:29,350 --> 00:29:31,310
they want to send an envoy

426
00:29:31,310 --> 00:29:32,590
to the capital.

427
00:29:32,590 --> 00:29:33,510
Is that it?

428
00:29:35,070 --> 00:29:36,200
Then let them come.

429
00:29:37,200 --> 00:29:39,070
Although the alliance is complete,

430
00:29:39,070 --> 00:29:41,920
our countries have been
at war for many years.

431
00:29:42,310 --> 00:29:44,110
Even if they come to pay tribute,

432
00:29:44,510 --> 00:29:45,960
it must follow the proper procedures

433
00:29:45,960 --> 00:29:47,880
and be carefully planned.

434
00:29:48,790 --> 00:29:50,310
So what do you suggest?

435
00:29:52,030 --> 00:29:53,290
I request Your Majesty

436
00:29:53,480 --> 00:29:56,540
to move to the Imperial Study
to discuss this in detail.

437
00:29:58,640 --> 00:29:59,830
I know

438
00:30:00,270 --> 00:30:03,070
tonight is Your Majesty's big day,

439
00:30:03,070 --> 00:30:04,800
and I shouldn't be saying this.

440
00:30:05,070 --> 00:30:05,830
But

441
00:30:06,240 --> 00:30:08,110
the country comes first.

442
00:30:09,070 --> 00:30:10,640
I believe Your Majesty

443
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:12,030
can understand.

444
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:13,830
Lord Zhang is right.

445
00:30:14,110 --> 00:30:15,840
Let's go to the Imperial Study.

446
00:30:38,680 --> 00:30:40,610
On the left is the Imperial Garden.

447
00:30:41,030 --> 00:30:43,090
On the right is the Imperial Kitchen.

448
00:30:45,590 --> 00:30:47,250
In the northwest corner is...

449
00:30:47,680 --> 00:30:49,880
Behind it is the Emperor's bedchamber.

450
00:31:04,110 --> 00:31:04,920
Who is there?

451
00:31:13,920 --> 00:31:14,920
Commander.

452
00:31:15,440 --> 00:31:16,750
In the middle of the night,

453
00:31:16,750 --> 00:31:18,150
what are you looking for?

454
00:31:18,750 --> 00:31:19,680
It's Lord Fei.

455
00:31:20,310 --> 00:31:22,960
I just saw a shadow flash by.

456
00:31:32,200 --> 00:31:33,590
There's nothing here.

457
00:31:34,440 --> 00:31:35,310
Commander,

458
00:31:35,640 --> 00:31:36,680
you must be seeing things.
